Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:20.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.41,0:00:22.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:29.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:40.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:43.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:49.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:55.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:02.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.74,0:01:07.08,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:09.31,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:16.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:26.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:30.23,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:35.77,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:41.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:48.71,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:53.19,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:55.17,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.53,0:01:59.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:02.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:06.22,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.91,0:02:09.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:11.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:14.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:15.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:19.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.20,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:29.00,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:35.45,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:39.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.16,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy \Nwhose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat crew landed \Non the Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to search for a ship coating craftsman \Nto help them reach Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the adventure, Camie, a mermaid \Nwho was with them, was kidnapped
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and about to be sold as a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, after storming the \Nauction house to save her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your squirming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Admiral Kizaru Takes Action! Sabaody \NArchipelago Thrown into Chaos"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! This town-- this \Nwhole archipelago-- is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy supposedly kicked \Na Celestial Dragon's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the auction house on Grove #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Kid and Law are there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Straw Hat bastard! \NWhat was he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he know that an admiral \Nfrom Navy Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will bring a warship here if \Nanyone hurts a Celestial Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has our ship been coated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was completed yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We set sail for Fish-Man Island immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just sit around \Nwhile an admiral shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in staying here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that dumbass's captain \Nis an even bigger dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever run into 'em in the \NNew World... I'll destroy 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Causing trouble with Navy Headquarters \Nwith the New World right in sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a truly troublesome lot they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on getting ready to set sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.74,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Right away, Captain Drake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then. Who's going to show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the situation, I somehow doubt \Nthis is an all-out arrest plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Straw Hat Luffy they're after, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd like to see what \Nan admiral is actually like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious, Apoo-san! \NLet's just get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hawkins! It's dangerous \Nhere! Let's set sail immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not destined to die today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:43.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Holy Land of Marie Jois"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat again?! It's one \Nthing after the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that entire family's bloodline?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reports indicate the presence \Nof the Straw Hat crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eustass Captain Kid and his crew, \Nand Trafalgar Law and his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen people with bounties \Nhave been confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of them, five are rookies \Nworth over 100 million each!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.27,0:07:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, the key offender \Nappears to be Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who assaulted the Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've lost contact with the \Nguards at the Human Shop--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,oh, I mean Employment Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe they may have all been subdued...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, this act of taking \Nthree Celestial Dragons hostage
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a vile and unprecedented transgression!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they made any demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, none at the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case may be, Sengoku-san, \Nwe'll need to take action
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,given that World Nobles are the victims here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kizaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to go. Rest easy; I won't be long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:59.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1420)}"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your shop, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Doflamingo...! \NWhere are you right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shop has lost all credibility, and \Nthen there's Roswald's family too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're definitely going to lash out at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.60,0:08:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something to fix things!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... Human trafficking \Nis so old-fashioned, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about smiles now! Smiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disco, I'm giving the shop to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't be callin' me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You're abandoning us during \Nthe worst crisis we've ever had?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, you annoying bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you sit there blaming \Nme for your own misfortune
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a "New Era" draws ever closer, Disco-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navy has given orders forcing \Nme-- no, us-- into active duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing this, what do you see \Non the horizon, Disco-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Whitebeard Pirates versus \Nthe Seven Warlords of the Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please evacuate as far away as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No watching, please! These \Nare dangerous people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The slave I bought is still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the mortars arrived yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, most of them! We're \Nhurrying to set them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has HQ said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.57,0:10:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Admiral Kizaru is coming, but \Nthe vanguard will consist of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of them?! They're coming here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! That's what they said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to remove your collar \Nnow. Are you ready, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, old man! Don't \Nbe crazy! It'll explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've seen a slave's collar explode before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bad idea! A very bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Franky is looking \Nfor the key as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should really wait until he \Nfinds it and brings it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Stop him, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Not here, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right. Just stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno what kind of power he used...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the one thing for sure is \Nthat he's no ordinary old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that somehow means it's okay \Nto leave Camie-chan in his hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What's Franky doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's too dangerous! \NIt won't come off without the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ringing! What're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, I told you! Now Camie's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this now?! \NDon't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your collar and handcuffs are already off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.70,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie! Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! I finally manage \Nto find 'em, but then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You found them? Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we no longer need them. \NHere, you carry this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... Th-Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the hell's going on \Nhere?! Who are you, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That geezer did something mysterious again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is that old guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the collar off barehanded?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, almost-slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the buyers took off! You \Nshould scram while you can, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that geezer took out these \Nguards all at once too,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then he must know how to use \Nmagic or some type of sorcery!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got powers or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said something about \Nyour straw hat, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That straw hat suits dauntless men very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know him, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know him! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he used what's called "Haki."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about it either, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, fellows. I didn't \Nrealize other pirates were watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be quite strong to have \Nwithstood that with no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to meet \Nsuch a big-shot here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dark King" Silvers Rayleigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it. What's a legendary \Nman doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On these islands I'm Ray-san, \Nthe coating craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go calling me that other name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an old soldier now. I just \Nwant to live in peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you'll survive, Hachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I told you all those times \Nnot to walk around these islands...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for saving my friend, fellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's this about wanting \Nto meet me, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's save that for later. \NWe first need to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have the place completely \Nsurrounded, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you criminals! Release \Nthe Roswald family at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An admiral will be arriving shortly! \NI recommend immediate surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame us for whatever \Nhappens, you rookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not only caught up in this, we're \Nbeing treated as accomplices now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a good glimpse of the insanity \Nthat makes Straw Hat Luffy so notorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no complaints, but I'd rather not \Nrun into an admiral now if I can avoid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'd prefer not to use that power of \Nmine anymore, so I leave this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be hard for me to stay settled \Ndown if the navy discovers who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of helping \Nout a senior citizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The longer we stay here, the \Nmore troops there'll be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm at it, I'll help you guys out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean things up outside, so don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.27,0:17:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who doesn't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can go back inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you even listening?! \NI told you two to stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what to do again and I'll start \Nby getting rid of you, Eustass-ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them are captains! \NThey're spearheading the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, worth 300 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eustass Captain Kid, worth 315 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law, worth 200 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay here and \Nbicker all you want. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can handle this all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them have bounties \Nwell over 100 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, they're so simpleminded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's gonna an all-out brawl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's use that chance to escape! We \Ncan't just sit around here anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks... I'm sorry for \Ncausing you trouble...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me! I'm just \Nglad you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie! It's my fault this happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have let you \Ngo to the amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll always cherish the memory \Nof going to the amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to apologize, Pappagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat said the same thing, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't one thing you \Nguys should be sorry for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of you are my friends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will rescue Camie, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.07,0:19:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's follow them. We're going \Nto break through in one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet up on Grove #13, should \Nwe find ourselves separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.33,0:19:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grove #13? Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't "got it" at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Mr. Giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all on the verge of becoming slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to flee somewhere \Nwith these people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Be careful not to \Ndraw attention to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man! Straw Hat's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will repay this favor if we \Never meet again! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking credit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mortars! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! All three of 'em have powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave enough people to rescue the \Nhostages, and gather all our men here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mortars, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready! Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't either of you do anything! \NYou'll just get in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you! Tell me what to do and--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Finger Net!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can stretch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of weird power is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.85,0:21:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was a goner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! You really are \Nscrewed up in the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start with Straw Hat Luffy! Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, you! Fire! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Stay sharp! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't falter! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.05,0:22:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.78,0:22:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.64,0:22:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toward himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.01,0:22:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be! Are these \Nguys really rookies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Admiral Kizaru arrived yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir! But I think he'll be here shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements from the navy \Npost have arrived, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! What's going on?! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh. There's a lot more than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:23:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sure got weird powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say yours is the weirdest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Swords are flying toward him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Marines are flying through \Nthe air, whirling, twirling...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are guns and even cannons \Nflying! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe my eyes! \NAnd I don't even have eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.04,0:23:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know Kid-san and Law-san had powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting interesting now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Break Through the Siege! The \NNavy vs. the Three Captains"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
